headline: EQT Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: EQT Corporation (NYSE: EQT) today announced that its Board of Directors declared a quarterly cash dividend on its common stock of $0.165 per share, payable on March 2, 2026, to shareholders of record at the close of business on February 17, 2026.

headline: BofA lists 5 best stocks as AI spending directly benefits Gas
summary: Investing.com -- Bank of America says investor rotation out of technology and into energy has intensified, but the move has largely bypassed natural gas producers, a gap the bank argues is increasingly attractive.
